WEBVTT

00:02.635 --> 00:04.330
Previously on The Vampire Diaries:

00:04.504 --> 00:06.836
For over a century,
I've lived in secret. Until now.

00:07.006 --> 00:10.601
- I know the risk. But I have to know her.
- Elena, a dead ringer for Katherine.

00:10.776 --> 00:13.370
You have no idea of the future
I have planned for us.

00:13.546 --> 00:15.173
You, me and Damon.

00:15.348 --> 00:17.782
Our love for Katherine
wasn't real, Damon.

00:17.950 --> 00:20.851
Katherine never compelled me.
I knew everything.

00:21.020 --> 00:23.250
I'm gonna bring her back.
Tell me how to get in the tomb.

00:23.422 --> 00:24.912
- The grimoire.
- Where is it?

00:25.091 --> 00:26.752
The journal. Johnathan Gilbert's.

00:26.926 --> 00:29.554
- Your ancestor's journal?
- I gave it to my teacher.

00:29.729 --> 00:30.889
- Alaric Saltzman.
- Damon.

00:31.097 --> 00:34.396
The grimoire, it was Emily's?
You need it to reverse the spell?

00:34.567 --> 00:35.591
- I'll help you.
- Okay.

00:35.768 --> 00:38.430
I told Damon
that I'd help him get Katherine back.

00:38.604 --> 00:40.629
- But it was a lie. I can't let him.
- Don't.

00:40.806 --> 00:42.535
I'll help you. Whatever it takes.

00:44.000 --> 00:50.074
